about_us_intro: We are Al Rasin Home Services Company
about_us_details: Raseen Recruitment Company is the official and authorized partner of Musaned. We strive to be the first choice in the field of mediation and the recruitment of skilled and qualified domestic workers. We do this by providing high-quality services to our clients with efficient and effective labor at competitive prices.To ensure this, we adopt a creative and innovative approach in finding suitable solutions for domestic labor services. We are meticulous in selecting workers, ensuring they meet the highest quality standards that serve the client's and family's interests during personal interviews and the nomination process, meeting our clients' expectations.In addition to our efficient services at competitive prices, we offer a quick and effective process, working to uphold the values of credibility and integrity, all while adhering to the regulations and laws of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.
about_us_professionals: We rely on a group of professional cleaning experts trained to the highest level of professionalism and speed in performance and execution.
